Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Henrietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Henrietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Henrietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Idiot! Where were you all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Louise. It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albion troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry! Everyone will be able to get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Masarini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened in the city of South Gotha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard our men started a rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they enemy had placed\Nsome kind of a magic item in our wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they're under an enemy spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Albion marched in during the chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have time to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was retreat here with Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did they recapture the city of South Gotha,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're also approaching our\Nposition with seventy thousand men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, there's no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please board the escape ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I shall board the last ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Queen of Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until everyone escapes safely, I have no intention of moving from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We finally made it back to Lowscythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to take care of the rearguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rearguard, you know, is the last line of defence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You basically have to resist the enemy force while everybody else escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an order from the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess isn't aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière, we need your strength in order to save the Queen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Cardinal, please, raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is to save Her Highness' life, I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... you... accepted it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming here with seventy thousand men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my Void magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Void?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't use it last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}this{\i0} time I might be able to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means saving the Princess' life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can save the Princess with my Void magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be no greater honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're telling you to be a bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're asking you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn down that mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something that only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, {\i1}I{\i0} have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our men don't have the strength to hold back seventy thousand men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you have to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just for the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maid and everyone else at the Fairy Inn might be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may get shamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honour to die for one's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make fun of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but is it that insignificant to die for everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I also want to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... the one I want to protect more than anyone else is{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get out of here, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to die staying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? Hey, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you aren't from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are... you saying that seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Okay. I won't stop you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my world, we have a toast and say goodbye at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are. Since it's this kind of a situation, no one will blame us for stealing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, it won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.55,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.17,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one request upon our farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is the last one after all, so I'll listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I want to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want to die unwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unsatisfactory to get married to you, but I won't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, as a proof that I existed, I want to at least get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could we buy this flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm closing the store anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Éclair D'amour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Éclair D'amour"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It doesn't matter what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that after this, a definite bond will form between Saito and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not one between master and familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do you do weddings here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't really know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss of oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no sense of delicacy to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take each other's hands and say our vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}M-{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}Me, too.{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were such a strange familiar and made me doubt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now, I'm glad it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she accepted the rearguard mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was searching for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure that she won't run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. To tell her to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess is important, but I'm more interested in the cute Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going... to meet the enemy of seventy thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think that dying for honour is a stupid thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't for honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I said "I love you" to Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't go now, I have a feeling that\Nthose words would lose their meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me want to say "I love you" to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from you won't make me happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Louise for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is outside of Lowcythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships will depart soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you guys reach the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancel the departure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get Louise back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go now, you'll lose your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't make Louise take my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die here, the matter will not end as a simple failure in tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our country will fall into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Masarini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to jump out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière's noble act would have been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Sleeping Beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stop the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun went to face Albion's troops alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to fight Albion by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were sleeping from the effects of a potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... he used that potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I gave it to Saito-san because I wanted him to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.23,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise-chan! It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me off! It isn't too late at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Saito die alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.09,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I have to turn into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your beloved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Del.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I... die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're going to die anyway, then do your best to act like a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you have point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner! Up front!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I regret not being able to do what comes after the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Éclair D'amour...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic flower that informs one of the condition of one's significant other even when they're far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that Saito-kun would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were saved because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend on doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crybaby Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let your familiar die because you went to the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ignoring Father's word against doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito died because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand firm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the big deal over some familiar's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "some familiar"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was special to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito was a special person to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a mistake to go to the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to go and die for the sake of my honour?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say it without hesitation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really you, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a ghost, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by a fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandalfr, the God's left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you should return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she took care of me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, her breasts were so huge, they surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were bigger than both Siesta's and Jessica's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... S-So you met a big-breasted fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do like big breasts, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You love huge breasts, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then keep living with the fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you for making me drink a sleeping potion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:21.71,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling! You were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, don't you think the enemy of seventy thousand was easier than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept believing... that you were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
